metadata.name: We love you Flannel
metadata.description:
This piece is a thank you from all of us 1/1 artists.  
You have been an amazing patron, collector, and friend!  
I can say that this space would not be the same without you, you fight for us and support us in ways we never imagined.  
Thank you Flannel, thank you for being there for us and changing our lives, and supporting our dreams!

From:  
Ilan Derech  
Holly Herbert  
Michelle Viljoen  
Nevin Johnson  
Tustont  
Lisanne Haack  
ADHD  
Rick Bakas  
Amir  
Philipp Rosenhain  
KIMO  
Maxwell N. Burnstein  
and all the other artists that you've supported!
